description.en-us: Hot Wheels Monster Trucks Oversized is a sub series of Hot Wheels Monster Trucks first launched in 2018 . This line features 1/24 scale versions of various Monster Truck models; they feature a special package design which can be used as a display case. The series gained its current name in 2021; prior to then, the series was simply known as Monster Trucks 1:24 Scale Trucks . Some trucks in this line have not been released in 1/64 scale form.
